  <Section title="Scorcherer Sets" emoji="üî•">
    <p>
      This is theoretically the highest damage set available. It utilizes Lord's Soul and Bloodlust
      to reach massive raw and affinity numbers. It maxes out every skill Lance wants, and as a
      bonus, grants Binding Counter and Scorcherer for free (we would most likely want to run these
      pieces even without those two skills).
    </p>

    <p>
      The transcended Guardian Rathalos allow us to max out the core skills and squeeze in a level
      of Scorcherer. Thanks to the recent buff that added fixed damage and lowered the cooldown,
      this skill is now quite powerful (even against fire resistant monsters).
    </p>

    <p>Binding counter is a nice raw damage boost, in matchups where we can proc it.</p>

